{"tid":99961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母 住樓上班仆街又漏水","createTime":"2017-01-29T15:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T16:15:45.000Z","uid":80513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aafe3b1f693a88b954682bd9b69461e8c15ded51","tid":99961,"uid":80513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:17:53.000Z","msg":"新年流流 預備開飯先見到個天花滲晒水<br />\n又聽到樓上baba聲爆水喉<br />\n即刻上去拍門又冇人應 (懷疑返左蝗國住）<br />\n叫大廈閘咸水制先滲少d<br />\n<br />\n頭先上去再望下就見到班仆街抹緊地<br />\n好聲好氣同佢講已經第n次搞到我地喇<br />\n條大陸閪又串串柒  嬲撚到我<br />\n<br />\n屋企先裝修好無耐 <br />\n想問下可以點追討佢賠償同要佢整撚番好條渠 咪撚再爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70348fe547524aa16b3dd56a933b12111797cac3","tid":99961,"uid":80513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:19:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5747b84a139ca21285b43dc5698832a0b5a2bbb4","tid":99961,"uid":80513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5598169272e7fdbf1589728a5f7f329ed9e25cd","tid":99961,"uid":80513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c4646bd0113dae4d94d94eb25647a2e2a44fa5","tid":99961,"uid":80513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:15:45.000Z","msg":"新年冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}